WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.200
External view: the arm starts above the three cubes.

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:04.600
It lowers toward the blue cube.

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:06.800
The gripper aligns around the blue cube.

00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:08.800
It closes and lifts the blue cube.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.800
The arm carries the blue cube across the workspace.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:13.710
It releases the cube and completes the correct blue pick.
